rows.label: qst101806_msg001
rows.name: LIST_QST101806仮実装

rows.label: qst101806_msg002
rows.name: 借金いっぱいしちゃった

rows.label: qst101806_msg003
rows.name: すぐ死ぬかなって思って

rows.label: qst101806_msg004
rows.name: そんなばかなも

rows.label: qst101806_msg005
rows.name: 逃げたジゾーを追いかけたい 一緒に連れてって

rows.label: qst101806_msg0001
rows.name: Hey, Gamedze! My Driver made it!

rows.label: qst101806_msg0002
rows.name: Is that right?

rows.label: qst101806_msg0003
rows.name:
Sorry for trouble 'cos
by my Blade Vahsah.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0004
rows.name:
He will give back money
you lend to him now.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0005
rows.name:
Oh! Came back with the money,
didya? Well, that's just splendid.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0006
rows.name: Indeedy!

rows.label: qst101806_msg0007
rows.name:
Here 5,000G. This cover silly
Vahsah's wild spending, yes?

rows.label: qst101806_msg0008
rows.name:
5,000G? Oh, I'm sorry, dearie.
That's a bit less than he owes.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0009
rows.name:
Huh? Not enough? How much
money Vahsah borrow?

rows.label: qst101806_msg0010
rows.name:
Ah, yeah... I guess I didn't
mention that part, did I?

rows.label: qst101806_msg0011
rows.name:
Just add a couple zeroes, and we'll
be sorted. 500,000G to be precise.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0012
rows.name:
Five wha-?!!! But that like...hundred
times hundred times hundred times...
Jizo cannot even count!

rows.label: qst101806_msg0013
rows.name:
You'll need to pay the whole
lot off in cash, dearie.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0014
rows.name:
Or, if you've got a decent lump of
that Divine Beast Quartz lying around,
I'd accept that as well! Hahah!

rows.label: qst101806_msg0015
rows.name: Divine Beast Quartz? What's that?

rows.label: qst101806_msg0016
rows.name:
Is very very precious jewel...
Sometimes found by salvage in Avaritia,
but only one time in million...

rows.label: qst101806_msg0017
rows.name:
Jizo not get hands on Divine
Beast Quartz, except in dream.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0018
rows.name:
Well, if this Blade can't pay me
back, there is one other thing
I'd accept. His Core Crystal!

rows.label: qst101806_msg0019
rows.name:
You'll get a pretty penny
for a Core Crystal in
somewhere like Superbia.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0020
rows.name: But that not possible to give!

rows.label: qst101806_msg0021
rows.name:
Vahsah only go back to Core
Crystal when Jizo dying!

rows.label: qst101806_msg0022
rows.name:
You only take Core Crystal over
Jizo's dead body! Literally!

rows.label: qst101806_msg0023
rows.name:
Don't turn your back on reality,
Jizo my pal. We're upstanding
people. We oughtta pay our debts.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0024
rows.name:
And I guess in this case that
means...uh, dying. Not a great
outcome, I'll admit.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0025
rows.name:
Well, well, well! These are
some generous friends you've
found yourselves here!

rows.label: qst101806_msg0026
rows.name:
I don't care who pays me, just
as long as someone does.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0027
rows.name:
But remember, it's 500 grand, or
a lump of Divine Beast Quartz! I
won't accept anything less!

rows.label: qst101806_msg0028
rows.name:
Thank you so much...
Sorry for big mess...
